entries.quest_dock_d: If the craft you have inspected containes the cargo you need, use the default '[' or ']' keys to cycle through their components to the engine slot.  After disabling the craft, pull up close and press the 'U' key to retreive the cargo.
entries.quest_inspect_d: While you have the objective craft targeted, use /inspect command to determine their cargo.
entries.quest_location_d: An area of Dathomir with known Witchblood activity

entries.title: Dathomir System: Disable and Inspect Witchblood Clan Soldiers
entries.title_d: Disable the Witchblood Clan Soldier and inspect him for information about a Witchblood Punisher rally
